# ImpactLedger Backend — API Reference

> **Base URL:** `http://localhost:8080`

## Global Response Wrapper

Every endpoint returns this wrapper:

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Optional message",   // may be null
  "data": { /* endpoint-specific payload */ }
}
```

On error:
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Error description",
  "data": null
}
```

## Authentication

- Uses **JWT Bearer tokens** (stateless, no sessions).
- Send the token in the `Authorization` header:  
  `Authorization: Bearer <token>`
- **Public endpoints** (no token needed): `/api/auth/**`, `/api/search/**`
- **All other endpoints require authentication.**

---

## 1. Auth (`/api/auth`)  🔓 Public

### 1.1 Register

| | |
|---|---|
| **Method** | `POST` |
| **URL** | `/api/auth/register` |
| **Content-Type** | `application/json` |
| **Auth** | ❌ Not required |

**Request Body:**

```json
{
  "email": "string",              // ✅ required
  "password": "string",           // ✅ required
  "userType": "NGO | CSR_INVESTOR", // ✅ required
  "phone": "string",              // optional

  // — NGO-specific fields (include when userType = "NGO") —
  "organizationName": "string",
  "registrationNumber": "string",
  "registrationType": ["12A", "80G"],
  "causeAreas": ["Education", "Healthcare"],
  "description": "string",
  "impactNarrative": "string",
  "geographicFocus": { "states": ["Maharashtra"], "districts": ["Pune"] },
  "contactInfo": { "address": "...", "website": "..." },

  // — CSR Investor-specific fields (include when userType = "CSR_INVESTOR") —
  "companyName": "string",
  "cin": "string",
  "annualCsrBudget": 5000000.00,
  "preferredCauseAreas": ["Education", "Health"],
  "preferredStates": ["Maharashtra", "Karnataka"]
}
```

**Response `data`:**

```json
{
  "token": "jwt-string",
  "userType": "NGO",
  "userId": "uuid",
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "name": "Organization Name",
  "profileId": "uuid",        // ngoId or investorId
  "verified": false
}
```

---

