## 3. Investor (`/api/investor`)  🔒 Authenticated

### 3.1 Get Dashboard

| | |
|---|---|
| **Method** | `GET` |
| **URL** | `/api/investor/dashboard` |
| **Auth** | ✅ Bearer token (user ID extracted from JWT) |

> No request params needed — the authenticated user's ID is pulled from the JWT token.

**Response `data`:**

```json
{
  "totalInvested": 15000000.00,
  "ngosSupported": 12,
  "projectsFunded": 8,
  "beneficiariesReached": 45000,
  "portfolio": [
    { "ngoName": "string", "amount": 1000000, "projectName": "string" }
  ],
  "recentActivity": [
    { "type": "FUNDED", "ngoName": "string", "amount": 500000, "date": "2026-03-01" }
  ],
  "causeAreaBreakdown": {
    "Education": 5000000.00,
    "Healthcare": 3000000.00
  }
}
```

