## 4. Compliance (`/api/compliance`)  🔒 Authenticated

### 4.1 Upload Receipt

| | |
|---|---|
| **Method** | `POST` |
| **URL** | `/api/compliance/upload-receipt` |
| **Content-Type** | `multipart/form-data` |
| **Auth** | ✅ Bearer token |

**Form Data:**

| Field | Type | Required | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| [file](file:///c:/Users/krish/impactledger-backend/impactledger-backend/src/main/java/com/impactledger/backend/controller/NgoController.java#24-29) | `File` | ✅ | Receipt image/PDF |
| `ngoId` | `UUID` | ✅ | NGO's unique ID |
| `projectId` | `UUID` | ❌ | Associated project ID |

**Frontend example (FormData):**

```javascript
const formData = new FormData();
formData.append('file', fileInput.files[0]);
formData.append('ngoId', 'uuid-string');
formData.append('projectId', 'uuid-string'); // optional

fetch('/api/compliance/upload-receipt', {
  method: 'POST',
  headers: { 'Authorization': 'Bearer ' + token },
  body: formData   // ⚠️ Do NOT set Content-Type manually
});
```

**Response `data`:**

```json
{
  "receiptId": "uuid",
  "ngoId": "uuid",
  "projectId": "uuid",
  "receiptType": "EXPENSE",
  "processingStatus": "PROCESSING",
  "extractedData": { "vendor": "...", "amount": 50000, "date": "2026-03-01" },
  "aiConfidence": 0.92,
  "imageUrl": "string",
  "createdAt": "2026-03-08T15:30:00"
}
```

---

