### 4.4 Generate Form 10BD

| | |
|---|---|
| **Method** | `POST` |
| **URL** | `/api/compliance/generate-form-10bd` |
| **Content-Type** | `application/json` |
| **Auth** | ✅ Bearer token |

**Request Body:**

```json
{
  "ngoId": "uuid",                    // ✅ required
  "receiptIds": ["uuid1", "uuid2"],   // ✅ required (array of UUIDs)
