}
```

**Response `data`:**

```json
{
  "formId": "uuid",
  "ngoId": "uuid",
  "formType": "FORM_10BD",
  "financialYear": "2025-26",
  "receiptIds": ["uuid1", "uuid2"],
  "generatedData": { /* structured form data */ },
  "downloadUrl": "string",
  "status": "GENERATED",
  "createdAt": "2026-03-08T15:30:00"
}
```

