## 5. Search (`/api/search`)  🔓 Public

### 5.1 Semantic Search

| | |
|---|---|
| **Method** | `POST` |
| **URL** | `/api/search/semantic` |
| **Content-Type** | `application/json` |
| **Auth** | ❌ Not required |

**Request Body:**

```json
{
  "query": "string",                   // ✅ required
  "causeAreas": ["Education"],         // optional — filter by cause areas
  "states": ["Maharashtra"],           // optional — filter by states
  "limit": 20                          // optional — default 20
}
```

**Response `data`:** Array of [SearchResultResponse](file:///c:/Users/krish/impactledger-backend/impactledger-backend/src/main/java/com/impactledger/backend/model/dto/response/SearchResultResponse.java#13-29):

```json
[
  {
    "ngoId": "uuid",
    "organizationName": "string",
    "description": "string",
    "impactNarrative": "string",
    "causeAreas": ["Education"],
    "geographicFocus": { "states": ["Maharashtra"] },
    "verificationStatus": "VERIFIED",
    "totalBeneficiaries": 5000,
    "totalFundingReceived": 2500000.00,
    "similarityScore": 0.89
  }
]
```

---

## 6. Voice (`/api/voice`)  🔒 Authenticated

### 6.1 Transcribe Audio

| | |
|---|---|
| **Method** | `POST` |
| **URL** | `/api/voice/transcribe` |
| **Content-Type** | `multipart/form-data` |
| **Auth** | ✅ Bearer token |

**Form Data:**

| Field | Type | Required | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| [file](file:///c:/Users/krish/impactledger-backend/impactledger-backend/src/main/java/com/impactledger/backend/controller/NgoController.java#24-29) | `File` | ✅ | Audio file |
| `languageCode` | `String` | ❌ | e.g. `"hi-IN"`, `"en-US"` |

**Frontend example:**

```javascript
const formData = new FormData();
formData.append('file', audioBlob, 'recording.webm');
formData.append('languageCode', 'hi-IN'); // optional

fetch('/api/voice/transcribe', {
  method: 'POST',
  headers: { 'Authorization': 'Bearer ' + token },
  body: formData
});
```

**Response `data`:**

```json
{
  "transcription": "Full transcribed text",
  "language": "hi-IN",
  "structuredData": { "donorName": "...", "amount": 50000 },
  "audioFeedbackUrl": "url-to-audio-feedback",
  "feedbackText": "Hindi confirmation text"
}
```

---

### 6.2 Synthesize Speech

| | |
|---|---|
| **Method** | `POST` |
| **URL** | `/api/voice/synthesize` |
| **Content-Type** | `application/json` |
| **Auth** | ✅ Bearer token |

**Request Body:**

```json
{
  "text": "string",                // ✅ required
  "languageCode": "hi-IN"         // optional — default "hi-IN"
}
```

**Response `data`:**

```json
{
  "audioUrl": "url-to-generated-audio"
}
```

