## Quick Reference Table

| # | Method | Endpoint | Auth | Content-Type |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | `POST` | `/api/auth/register` | ❌ | `application/json` |
| 2 | `POST` | `/api/auth/login` | ❌ | `application/json` |
| 3 | `POST` | `/api/auth/verify-otp` | ❌ | `application/json` |
| 4 | `GET` | `/api/ngo/profile/{ngoId}` | ✅ | — |
| 5 | `PUT` | `/api/ngo/profile/{ngoId}` | ✅ | `application/json` |
| 6 | `GET` | `/api/ngo/{ngoId}/projects` | ✅ | — |
| 7 | `POST` | `/api/ngo/projects` | ✅ | `application/json` |
| 8 | `GET` | `/api/investor/dashboard` | ✅ | — |
| 9 | `POST` | `/api/investor/express-interest` | ✅ | `application/json` |
| 10 | `POST` | `/api/compliance/upload-receipt` | ✅ | `multipart/form-data` |
| 11 | `GET` | `/api/compliance/receipt/{receiptId}/status` | ✅ | — |
| 12 | `GET` | `/api/compliance/receipts?ngoId=` | ✅ | — |
| 13 | `POST` | `/api/compliance/generate-form-10bd` | ✅ | `application/json` |
| 14 | `GET` | `/api/compliance/forms?ngoId=` | ✅ | — |
| 15 | `GET` | `/api/compliance/form/{formId}/preview` | ✅ | — |
| 16 | `POST` | `/api/search/semantic` | ❌ | `application/json` |
| 17 | `POST` | `/api/voice/transcribe` | ✅ | `multipart/form-data` |
| 18 | `POST` | `/api/voice/synthesize` | ✅ | `application/json` |

> [!TIP]
> For `multipart/form-data` requests (receipt upload & voice transcribe), do **not** manually set the `Content-Type` header — let the browser set it automatically so the boundary is included.
